et access Please note that email and phone services on Post will continue to operate normally  as will other on Post network services  Incoming and outgoing email messages will be  held  and delivered when Internet connectivity is restored  In the event of an emergency the VMI Mass Notification System will continue to operate as expected  Should you need to call 911 during this time  please do so from a cell phone  Contact the Help Desk at Help vmi edu or call 7643 if you have any questions  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 